parcel.name: Satoshi Cinema
parcel.label: theater
parcel.description:
Satoshi Cinema 
Is a Event space located on the cryptovoxel's island of Satoshi 
Featuring a large 38 seat movie theater, concession stand, space for up to 8 mini art exhibits 
And upstairs lounge

The purpose of the DAO is to manage the space and create community minded events

http://satoshi-cinema.io/ - http://discord.gg/TNyaU9Bmht
